net.fortuna.ical4j.model

Class ComponentFactoryImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.AbstractContentFactory<ComponentFactory>
      • net.fortuna.ical4j.model.ComponentFactoryImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class ComponentFactoryImpl
extends AbstractContentFactory<ComponentFactory>
    $Id$ [05-Apr-2004]

    A factory for creating iCalendar components. Note that if relaxed parsing is enabled (via specifying the system property: icalj.parsing.relaxed=true) illegal component names are allowed.
